  "description": "This Blackjack game allows from 1 to 5 players and uses pre-defined rules from Las Vegas, Downtown Vegas, Reno and Atlantic City.  There is also a custom mode where you can define your own rules.  Minimum and maximum bets are customizable as are the number of decks to be used.\nThe game includes a hint mode for the novice player that will tell you the optimal play at any given moment and also includes an optimal play chart you can take with you when you're ready to hit the real casinos.\n",
